{"tid":484500,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"講下你哋老豆/老母鐘意玩咩電話game","createTime":"2017-11-30T06:43:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-30T10:23:34.000Z","uid":34701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"d88814e1db23bd4e315307cca590be41d69f214b","tid":484500,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:43:17.000Z","msg":"有冇巴絲老豆/老母鐘意打機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日出街都見到啲師奶喺度玩Candy Crush，唔知係咪多數上咗年紀嘅都鐘意玩呢隻呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28a3511da9aca701a5af4b444c36055f90d5e388","tid":484500,"uid":12471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:51:05.000Z","msg":"FGO"},{"pid":"c327e2d5ce561568a8d36680f255d5ba6c93c9a2","tid":484500,"uid":148082,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:52:03.000Z","msg":"Candy Crush"},{"pid":"a13f704aaa539679f333944e60a0bb6f5c6f4181","tid":484500,"uid":90766,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"全家pad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地仲要開大聲，每晚食完飯都係無限轉珠聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a058ac469d80a3b59ba8d8593dea663df44298","tid":484500,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T06:59:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全家pad<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地仲要開大聲，每晚食完飯都係無限轉珠聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起都嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知點解啲老嘢一定要開到最大聲睇片/打機，就算喺街都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ca919c604b5054b96e3c4e47ca798999b678be","tid":484500,"uid":12618,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:04:12.000Z","msg":"卡通農場<br />\n個icon係隻雞頭<br />\n我老母玩到好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0c5064b0ba4306e534e496926dce518d76cc4ed","tid":484500,"uid":61917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:07:50.000Z","msg":"Tsum tsum<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ae793f3322b740c5afb14e8a2fbb5139f2862d","tid":484500,"uid":33162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"Pok&eacute;mon go <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"053cdab85c0f8a79e507e18699daad2ec348d656","tid":484500,"uid":56240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"pubg"},{"pid":"9530a1c133c77f29f5a5828581a3b4dafc4d1667","tid":484500,"uid":86893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:12:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾支那課金game<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4278a3e05ee965676e3d22f2ec6bd9b5ad4ce2c","tid":484500,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:15:24.000Z","msg":"係條街見最多中佬打牌，麻雀。仲有咩地主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08919bf22cbed016a8a75471d7538f2a7c810c9","tid":484500,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Pok&eacute;mon go <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仲有玩其實都要讚下佢嘅恆心同毅力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利伸: 仲玩緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f48d1270c9d2198f4cd8c7d8e9ec292f05a6c84","tid":484500,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:16:08.000Z","msg":"鬥地主"},{"pid":"6316cd482fb67977bac7afce3cf8e172a3d27ce2","tid":484500,"uid":57488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:16:31.000Z","msg":"Twenty"},{"pid":"97736b12c9e9d9d8b4118749524c60e3393a218e","tid":484500,"uid":1858,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:53:39.000Z","msg":"博雅德洲撲克<br />\n<br />\n我老豆份人好撚守舊，真係好少用電子野，直至6,7年前佢見我係facebook玩就改變左佢一生。初頭佢都係日日坐係我隔離睇我玩，因為正如我所講，佢份人好守舊好大男人，所以佢唔會出聲話好想玩，教下我之類，同時佢又真係好鍾意賭錢。咁我難得見佢咁有恆心日日睇我玩（佢好少可會留意人做乜，仲要一段時間咁耐）咪主動教佢，當然最初佢就口硬話唔洗，但係口裡說不，其實只係欲拒還迎，玩到依家。<br />\n<br />\n近年有得用電話玩，我教埋佢開擴音屌人老母等自己輸左都有得發洩下，唔洗屈係個心到。最重要係自此之後，我打緊機佢都唔會再催我依飯，打機打到講曬粗口佢都唔會再話我發癲發神經，因為佢仲激過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af97ec75cb7ad108ae861c8bd93350853a5d5c1b","tid":484500,"uid":31180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>卡通農場<br />\n個icon係隻雞頭<br />\n我老母玩到好激動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都好鍾意玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啲動物好撚cute"},{"pid":"9fb87bcf572564aeb9548a3ed330e2acc9dba8e6","tid":484500,"uid":34701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T09:46:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67648ce637ae16e12642c3977a479b0d2f21cc8e","tid":484500,"uid":149878,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-30T10:23:34.000Z","msg":"糖果粉碎"}]}